<h2 id="_example_of_use">4. Example of use</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>This service for shortening URLs is e.g. used for automatic tweets that are generated via the <a href="/en/omni-channel/online-store/extras/live-shopping#100"><strong>Procedure manager</strong></a>. In this case, the URLs of the category pages will automatically be shortened, e.g. for the <strong>Tweet live shopping offers</strong> procedure. This way, more characters will be left for the rest of the message.</p>
</div>
